article/.premium/knesset-advances-bill-to-fire-academics-for-views-seen-as-supporting-terror-by-govt/00000190-9e04-d03e-a5fd-9fb6744f0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么民主党和共和党在以色列和加沙问题上的纲领如此模糊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-10/ty-article/.highlight/why-the-democratic-and-gop-platforms-on-israel-and-gaza-are-so-vague/00000190-9dab-dbad-adfc-fdbbef040000</link><description>在目前尚不清楚拜登的连任竞选活动是否能维持足够的支持度过一周之际，围绕拜登以色列政策的细微差别的任何辩论都无关紧要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 18:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-10/ty-article/.highlight/why-the-democratic-and-gop-platforms-on-israel-and-gaza-are-so-vague/00000190-9dab-dbad-adfc-fdbbef040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有赢得加沙战争。它的其他战争也没有那么成功</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-not-won-the-gaza-war-its-other-wars-werent-so-successful-either/00000190-9caf-da1a-adf0-9ebfc5720000</link><description>历史上第二长的战争已经过去九个月了，以色列是否擅长战争是一个令人烦恼的问题，并提出了巨大的问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:24:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-not-won-the-gaza-war-its-other-wars-werent-so-successful-either/00000190-9caf-da1a-adf0-9ebfc5720000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡如何系统性地挫败哈马斯释放人质的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-netanyahu-has-systematically-foiled-talks-to-release-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/00000190-9b91-d591-a7ff-fff341120000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-netanyahu-has-systematically-foiled-talks-to-release-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/00000190-9b91-d591-a7ff-fff341120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 278 天：内塔尼亚胡表示，如果不跨越“红线”，他承诺停战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-278-netanyahu-says-committed-to-truce-if-it-doesnt-cross-red-lines/00000190-9d7f-dbad-adfc-fdff54ad0001</link><description>由摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团前往卡塔尔参加休战峰会，参与峰会的官员称其为“决定性的”。 ■ 人质家属踏上从耶路撒冷前往特拉维夫的为期三天的游行。 ■ 加沙的报道称，以色列对流离失所者营地的袭击造成 29 人死亡，主要是妇女和儿童 ■ 以色列国防军表示，约有 30 枚火箭从黎巴嫩发射到以色列北部 ■ 战争进入 278 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:45:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-278-netanyahu-says-committed-to-truce-if-it-doesnt-cross-red-lines/00000190-9d7f-dbad-adfc-fdff54ad0001</guid></item><item><title>最新的空中情报：真主党在以色列境内的镜头中最可怕的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/up-to-date-aerial-intel-the-scariest-lesson-from-hezbollahs-footage-of-inside-israel/00000190-9cf9-d41c-abfc-defd5de40000</link><description>多架无人机的航拍照片显示，真主党拥有实时的打击情报。发表后，它袭击了戈兰高地的纳法赫基地，造成两名平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/up-to-date-aerial-intel-the-scariest-lesson-from-hezbollahs-footage-of-inside-israel/00000190-9cf9-d41c-abfc-defd5de40000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质起诉在加沙雇佣巴勒斯坦劫持者的美国非营利组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</link><description>该诉讼称，该组织的领导人“故意并故意获取和传播哈马斯的宣传”，并“物质上支持”哈马斯的恐怖主义行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</guid></item><item><title>资产还是负债？民主党制定选举纲领，以色列仍是热点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/asset-or-liability-israel-remains-flash-point-as-democrats-draw-up-election-platform/00000190-9c0f-d328-a9d1-9dff2dd00000</link><description>周二的在线听证会上，中东问题上的民主分歧十分明显，亲巴勒斯坦不承诺运动的一名领导人呼吁美国停止对以色列的军事援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 14:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/asset-or-liability-israel-remains-flash-point-as-democrats-draw-up-election-platform/00000190-9c0f-d328-a9d1-9dff2dd00000</guid></item><item><title>谁说以色列人不能灵活变通？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-said-israelis-cant-be-flexible/00000190-97db-d590-affd-b7df48920000</link><description>以色列人将柔术训练（突破精神和身体极限）视为治愈和赋权的源泉</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 14:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-said-israelis-cant-be-flexible/00000190-97db-d590-affd-b7df48920000</guid></item><item><title>这些以色列士兵在10月7日受伤。这就是他们现在的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/going-back-to-israeli-soldiers-wounded-on-october-7-the-trauma-isnt-over/00000190-9c3b-d262-a9f4-dfbf67260000</link><description>《国土报》再次探访了 10 月 7 日受伤的四名以色列士兵，了解他们的艰辛旅程。 “如果我在前三周没有得到支持，我想我今天就不会站在这里”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 12:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/going-back-to-israeli-soldiers-wounded-on-october-7-the-trauma-isnt-over/00000190-9c3b-d262-a9f4-dfbf67260000</guid></item><item><title>随着战斗加剧，以色列命令加沙城的巴勒斯坦人向南撤离至代尔巴拉赫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-on-all-residents-of-gaza-city-to-evacuate-south-to-deir-al-balah/00000190-9bfb-d872-a3b5-fffb929e0000</link><description>据加沙人称，以色列军队加大对加沙城周边社区的攻击力度后，数万人再次流离失所，与战争开始时的情况类似。一位居民告诉《国土报》：“当时还有地方可去，但现在从北到南一切都被摧毁了”</descripti